<template>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" :height="IconSize" :width="IconSize" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        
        <title />
        <g data-name="Layer 19" id="Layer_19">
            <path style="fill: #101820"  d="M16,17a8,8,0,1,1,8-8A8,8,0,0,1,16,17ZM16,3a6,6,0,1,0,6,6A6,6,0,0,0,16,3Z" />
            <path style="fill: #101820" 
                d="M23,31H9a5,5,0,0,1-5-5V22a1,1,0,0,1,.49-.86l5-3a1,1,0,0,1,1,1.72L6,22.57V26a3,3,0,0,0,3,3H23a3,3,0,0,0,3-3V22.57l-4.51-2.71a1,1,0,1,1,1-1.72l5,3A1,1,0,0,1,28,22v4A5,5,0,0,1,23,31Z" />
        </g>
    </svg>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: 'ProfileIcon',
        props:{
            size:{
                type:String,
                require:false
            },
            color:{
                type:String,
                require:false
            }
        },
        data(){
            return{
                IconSize:null,
                IconColor:null,
            }
        },
        mounted(){
            this.getSize();
            this.getColor();
        },
        methods:{
            getSize(){
                if (this.$props.size){
                    this.IconSize=this.$props.size
                    return
                }
                this.IconSize="30px"
                return
            },
            getColor(){
                if (this.$props.color){
                    this.IconColor=this.$props.color
                    return
                }
                this.IconColor="#000000"
                return
            },
            deletePost(){
                this.$emit("AddPost")
            }
        },
    }
</script>
